{"tid":2118312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君：新一輪個案呈單一病毒株 料源自同一爆發點","createTime":"2020-07-21T11:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T11:52:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a33f2d743f9ba7172eaa7fa6f042f22c799bae","tid":2118312,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"張竹君：新一輪個案呈單一病毒株 料源自同一爆發點<br />\n發佈時間 2020-07-21 18:22最後更新時間 2020-07-21 18:22<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，衛生防護中心近日邀請了香港大學專家，分析本港新一輪新型冠狀病毒的病毒株，發現坪石邨彬記粥麵店群組、慈雲山港泰護老中心群組，以及最近個案都呈單一病毒株，相信個案是源自同一個爆發點，可能是從的士司機或黃大仙社區，經一些餐廳群組慢慢散出來。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君說，政府針對四類高危人士進行病毒檢測，暫時未發現有的士司機確診。她又指，任何地方，包括香港，防疫措施一放鬆，就自然會有個案爆發；但若要長期收緊措施，社會亦未必守得住。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348278&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2b56eabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348278</a>"},{"pid":"65a20717a395f57d84fa4d003b4f72855caf52b8","tid":2118312,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ec756e6489f76d6e9f776a55e8606f354373949","tid":2118312,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"將臣，真祖"},{"pid":"40e1d08bee30a2d1b376c425e9e023966eec888d","tid":2118312,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"呀雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2b29f2a34533b3db421217345d059317ff0282","tid":2118312,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c56c41ab01f53b187db93b7eec20dbe23127cc9","tid":2118312,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s